          <h3>Drop in. Walk away.</h3>
          <p>Single LWPE20 SKU covers shed walls, barn doorways, side-entry doors, walk-up canopies, and small commercial entries. Compact 5.35"&nbsp;×&nbsp;8.70" housing fits a standard 4" J-box. <strong>Integrated photocell standard</strong> — dusk-to-dawn out of the box, no controls package, no add-on photocell upgrade. Up to <strong>2,750 lm at 20W · 4000K (139 lm/W peak efficacy)</strong>. 5-year warranty.</p>
